  "NEOW.talk.PRISM_MOD_CHARACTER_PRISM_CHARACTER.2-2.ancient": "그러면... 부서질 때까지... 오르거라...",
  "NEOW.talk.PRISM_MOD_CHARACTER_PRISM_CHARACTER.3-0.ancient": "나는... 너를 부른 적이 없다...",
  "NEOW.talk.PRISM_MOD_CHARACTER_PRISM_CHARACTER.3-0.next": "...",
  "NEOW.talk.PRISM_MOD_CHARACTER_PRISM_CHARACTER.3-1.char": "*물러서지 않는 소리*",
  "NEOW.talk.PRISM_MOD_CHARACTER_PRISM_CHARACTER.3-1.next": "...",
  "NEOW.talk.PRISM_MOD_CHARACTER_PRISM_CHARACTER.3-2.ancient": "그렇다면... 네 선택의 무게를... 짊어져라...",
  "NEOW.talk.PRISM_MOD_CHARACTER_PRISM_CHARACTER.4-0r.ancient": "아직도... 돌아가지 않는가...",
