  "NEOW.pages.INITIAL.options.PRISM_SILENCE.description": "니오우는 아무것도 주지 않습니다.",

  "OROBAS.talk.PRISM_MOD_CHARACTER_PRISM_CHARACTER.0-0.ancient": "삼각형 내려왔다?! 왜 내려왔다?!",
  "OROBAS.talk.PRISM_MOD_CHARACTER_PRISM_CHARACTER.0-0.next": "...",
  "OROBAS.talk.PRISM_MOD_CHARACTER_PRISM_CHARACTER.0-1.char": "*지루한 울음소리*",
  "OROBAS.talk.PRISM_MOD_CHARACTER_PRISM_CHARACTER.0-1.next": "...",
  "OROBAS.talk.PRISM_MOD_CHARACTER_PRISM_CHARACTER.0-2.ancient": "지루하다?! 논다! 나랑 논다!",
  "OROBAS.talk.PRISM_MOD_CHARACTER_PRISM_CHARACTER.1-0.ancient": "또 왔다! 삼각형 또 내려왔다!",
  "OROBAS.talk.PRISM_MOD_CHARACTER_PRISM_CHARACTER.1-0.next": "...",
  "OROBAS.talk.PRISM_MOD_CHARACTER_PRISM_CHARACTER.1-1.char": "*덜 지루한 울림*",
  "OROBAS.talk.PRISM_MOD_CHARACTER_PRISM_CHARACTER.1-1.next": "...",
  "OROBAS.talk.PRISM_MOD_CHARACTER_PRISM_CHARACTER.1-2.ancient": "좋다! 오늘은 조금 더 논다!",
  "OROBAS.talk.PRISM_MOD_CHARACTER_PRISM_CHARACTER.2-0.ancient": "삼각형, 이제 안 무섭다. 조금 반짝인다.",
  "OROBAS.talk.PRISM_MOD_CHARACTER_PRISM_CHARACTER.2-0.next": "...",
  "OROBAS.talk.PRISM_MOD_CHARACTER_PRISM_CHARACTER.2-1.char": "*희미한 긍정의 소리*",
  "OROBAS.talk.PRISM_MOD_CHARACTER_PRISM_CHARACTER.2-1.next": "...",
  "OROBAS.talk.PRISM_MOD_CHARACTER_PRISM_CHARACTER.2-2.ancient": "그래! 친구 비슷하다! 아마도!",
  "OROBAS.talk.PRISM_MOD_CHARACTER_PRISM_CHARACTER.3-0.ancient": "오늘도 내려왔다! 기다렸다!",
  "OROBAS.talk.PRISM_MOD_CHARACTER_PRISM_CHARACTER.3-0.next": "...",
  "OROBAS.talk.PRISM_MOD_CHARACTER_PRISM_CHARACTER.3-1.char": "*따뜻한 진동*",
