  "OROBAS.talk.PRISM_MOD_CHARACTER_PRISM_CHARACTER.7-1.char": "*뿌듯한 울음소리*",
  "OROBAS.talk.PRISM_MOD_CHARACTER_PRISM_CHARACTER.7-1.next": "...",
  "OROBAS.talk.PRISM_MOD_CHARACTER_PRISM_CHARACTER.7-2.ancient": "좋다! 오로바스도 좋은 친구다!",
  "OROBAS.talk.PRISM_MOD_CHARACTER_PRISM_CHARACTER.8-0.ancient": "삼각형, 오늘은 어디까지 오른다?",
  "OROBAS.talk.PRISM_MOD_CHARACTER_PRISM_CHARACTER.8-0.next": "...",
  "OROBAS.talk.PRISM_MOD_CHARACTER_PRISM_CHARACTER.8-1.char": "*자신 있는 진동*",
  "OROBAS.talk.PRISM_MOD_CHARACTER_PRISM_CHARACTER.8-1.next": "...",
  "OROBAS.talk.PRISM_MOD_CHARACTER_PRISM_CHARACTER.8-2.ancient": "그럼 간다! 오로바스도 마음만 같이 간다!",

